Package: visualRPlots
Title: Nice ggplot2-based functions for data representation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Garcia", "Juan Manuek", , "juan.garciai@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This ggplot2-based library contains several functions to be used 
to generate plots of diverse data types. In addition, it also includes functions to 
perform and represent results of Principal Component Analysis (PCA) and t-distributed
stochastic neighbor embedding (t-SNE).
